Select PLN_CD, DDMMYYYY, DAY_WEK, WEEK_NO from PRD010 where DDMMYYYY >= ':1' and DDMMYYYY <=':2' and OPE_TYP > '0' and length(rtrim(PLN_CD)) = 6 and PLN_CD >= NVL(':3',' ') and PLN_CD <= ':4' order by PLN_CD, DDMMYYYY

Select distinct P20.PLN_CD, P20.PLN_MY, P20.MTOCD, P20.COL_CD, P20.COLI_CD, P18.PLN_SEQ4 from PRD020 P20, PRD018 P18 where P20.PLN_MY = ':1' and P18.PLN_MY = ':2' and P20.PLN_CD = ':3' and P18.PLN_CD = P20.PLN_CD and P18.MTOCD = P20.MTOCD and P18.COL_CD = P20.COL_CD and P18.COLI_CD = P20.COLI_CD order by P20.PLN_CD, P20.PLN_MY, P18.PLN_SEQ4
